snippet.title: Cat Box Paradox Trailer
snippet.description:
Cat Box Paradox is a new platform game coming soon to PC on Steam and itch.io

Dead?... Alive?...Both? Help Einstein the cat restore reality before his owners come home to a dangerously unstable alternate dimension.

In this fast paced retro platform game, you must think quick as you run, jump and swap colour, making your way through 8 floors of challenging colour changing mayhem.
